Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ Gems ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ We'll always save the day ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.67,0:00:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Steven: ¶ And if you think\Nwe can't, we'll ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ Always find a way ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ That's why the people ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.79,0:00:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ Of this world ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.88,0:00:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ Believe in ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,¶ Garnet ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Amethyst: ¶ Amethyst ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Pearl: ¶ And Pearl ¶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.97,0:00:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Insects buzz ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚看到了吗？\NDid you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,咣当！嘭的一下！\NWapoosh!\NJust wapoosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒啊，紫晶\NThat's great, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你进步的真快\NYou're getting so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.10,0:00:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不！刚才那下糟透了！\NNo! This is worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.65,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天早上的时候它还发出嗖的声音！\NThis morning,\Nit was like wsshh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,嗖的一下！快极了，嗖，嗖嗖！\NJust wsshh! Superfast,\Nlike wsshh, wsshh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯哼\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想你今天\NI think this is why
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,休息一下会比较好\Na day off would be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能总是想着\NYou should take a break
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.37,0:00:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么做掉铁石英\Nfrom obsessing over Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，你确定我们必须今天去那里？\NUgh, are you sure we have to do this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.96,0:00:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,当然！\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,拜访一下橄榄石和青金石会很有趣的！\NVisiting Peridot and Lapis will be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，一说到“有趣”，我马上能联想到青金石\NYeah, 'cause when I think "fun," I think Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道她们最近在做什么\NI wonder\Nwhat they're up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.50,0:00:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可能已经把对方都逼疯了吧\NMaybe they drove each other crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.72,0:01:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,然后一把火把谷仓烧了\Nand burnt the barn down.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,喔啊\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,她们的确对谷仓做了不少改动\NThey sure did something to the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.48,0:01:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，波莱特，我需要你.\NBut, Paulette, I need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，快放手吧，佩西\NOh, get over it,Percy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,换个人做友谊手环吧\NGo make another friendship bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.82,0:01:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是嘛\NSeriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.65,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石，橄榄石，嗨！\NLapis, Peridot, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.74,0:01:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文！\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.66,0:01:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,又见面真是太好了！\NIt's so good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是，青金石\NYou, too, Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶！\NAmethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.19,0:01:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你今天看上去有所不同啊\NSomething looks different about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么不同？\NLike what?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.83,0:01:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,和上次见面时比\NHave you grown taller
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.67,0:01:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你好像长高了？\Nsince the last timeI saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没，还很矮\NNope, still short.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.66,0:01:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢\NYou're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦\NFor the joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.38,0:01:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦，你们看上去真不错\NWow. You guys\Nare looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我超喜欢你们对谷仓的改动\NAnd I love what you did to the barn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,嗷，我知道它很棒\NAw, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但等等，等等！\NBut wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.10,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们一定要看看谷仓的内部！\NYou guys have to see the inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,青金石，带我们飞进去！\NLapis, fly us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.69,0:01:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.72,0:01:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来的我们母星外的家\NWelcome to our home away from Homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.64,0:01:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喔啊！\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你们把墙壁做成了水族箱！\NYou made the wall\Nan aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.03,0:01:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,呃呃呃！\NEww!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你们刻意做的这些装修？\NYou did all this stuff on purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，简直像你们把东西随便扔一堆\NLike, you didn't just knock over a bunch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,然后说“呃，以后再收拾”\Nof paint cans and go,"Enh, just leave it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哦不，整个谷仓的装修都是非常有意义的\NOh, no. This was all very intentional.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的，当时我有个主意：既然我们可以用声音创作音乐\NYou see, I had this idea:"What if we made music,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那为什么不可以用物体创作呢？\Nbut, instead of sounds,we used things?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,真是蠢透了\NThat's dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们，这是艺术！\NGuys, that's art!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艺术？\NArt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,听上去好蠢！\NThat sounds ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直都管这些东西叫“咪嗼”\NI've been calling it meep morp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.47,0:02:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,给你看看我们的嗼嗼\NLet us show you\Nour morps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个作品叫“哇，谢谢”\NThis piece is called Wow, Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,它表达了人们因为沟通的隔阂而挣扎\NIt represents the struggles of intercommunication.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.82,0:02:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,录音带是将我们两人的经历\NThe tape is the ribbon that binds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,连结在一起的桥梁\Nour experienceon Earth together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,它没什么实用意义\NIt has no functional purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.52,0:02:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,只是能让我心里难受而已\NIt just makes me feel bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的咪嗼\NHere's my meep morp.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,它是个球棒\NThis is a baseball bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,它让我想起了玩棒球的时光\NIt reminds me of when I played baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是史蒂文给我的树叶\NThis is the leaf Steven gave me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,它让我想起…史蒂文给了我一片树叶\NIt reminds me of the time Steven...gave me a leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，对啊，我也记得！\NHey, yeah, it reminds me of that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉被囚禁了\NI just feel trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉被囚禁了\NI just feel trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这是表达那几千年\NIs this one about the thousands of years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你被困在镜子中的事吗？\Nyou spent trapped in a mirror?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.58,0:03:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是很喜欢那个电视剧\NI just really like that show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.18,0:03:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，紫晶，你会爱死这个的.\NOh, Amethyst,you'll love this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧\NCheck it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一堆马桶？\NThey're toilets?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没错！\NRight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.56,0:03:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢想我还能有什么好点子\NWhat will I think of next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这代表了我被关在\NThis represents the time I spent imprisoned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你卫生间里的那段时光，史蒂文\Nin your bathroom, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我管它叫“有人使用”\NI call it Occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.40,0:03:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是一部合作品\NIt's a collaborative piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真是太精彩了\NIt's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你不需要明白啊\NWhat's there to get?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是水！\NIt's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,从马桶里喷出来的水！\NShooting out of toilets!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我在家里也能看到啊\NI can see that at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.84,0:03:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，我知道你觉得这挺没意思的\NAll right. I see you're not impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,但这个——别激动\NBut this -- hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,它——这就是我们一直在等的压轴戏\NThis -- this is what we've all been waiting for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.49,0:03:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,加上我控制金属的能力\NWith the power of my metal abilities,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,它会让你们惊得裙子都飞走的！\NI will impress the shirts right off of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,嗒哒！\NTa-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个单石乐队！\NIt's a one-Gem metal band.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,一呀，二呀，三呀，开始…\NOne, a-two, a-three, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛，我就练习了这么多\NWelp, that's as far as I've practiced that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.53,0:04:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不试试一次只用一个乐器呢？\NWhy don't you try one thing at a time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.67,0:04:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们有客人啊，青金石\NBecause we have guests, Lapis,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.48,0:04:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得让客人们高兴！\Nguests who must be impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.62,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以一起表演\NWe can try it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.68,0:04:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,¶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,¶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这难道不是很棒吗？\NIsn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.83,0:04:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧她们一直在做这么酷的东西\NLook at all this cool stuff they're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.44,0:04:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这些东西算什么！\NThis is all nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她们一直都在谷仓里玩破烂\NThey've been out here playing with garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不是很喜欢玩破烂吗？\NBut you love playing with garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早就不玩了\NNot anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.04,0:04:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,谁有时间浪费在这些破烂上？！铁石英还在外面游荡呢？！\NWho has time for any that when Jasper is out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,¶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，紫晶\NAh, Amethyst,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我，呃，尽量别在这里\NI, uh, try not to use the J-word
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,随便说铁某的名字\Nso loosely around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去做点更有意义的事了\N[sigh] I'm gonna go do\Nsomething useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦，紫晶看上去完全无法理解嗼嗼！\NWow, Amethyst doesn't seem to understand morps at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不，她是因为其他原因不高兴的\NNo, it's something else:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶发现\NAmethyst found out
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,她本应该是铁石英那样高大的战士\Nshe's supposed to be just like Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,咩？\NMeh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.27,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,前几天她被铁石英的打得惨败\NJasper took her down in a fight and, now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这些天她一直想着怎样打回去\Nshe's obsessed with getting a rematch,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.94,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来证明她足够好\Nto prove she's good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.55,0:05:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶，小晶晶，紫老大\NAmethyst,Ams, Big A.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.74,0:05:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你比铁石英强太多了\NYou are way better than Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.82,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.24,0:05:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.53,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你都告诉她什么了？\NWhat did you tell her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我，呃…\NI, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是想啥呢，干嘛把自己跟铁石英比？\NWhat are you even doing,comparing yourself to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,哦紫晶，这太荒谬了\NOh, Amethyst,that's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该叫你荒谬晶\NI should call you Ridiculousthyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哈！呀！\NHah! Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是认真的，紫晶和铁石英\NI mean, seriously,Amethyst and Jasper
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是两种完全不同的石英\Nare two completely different Quartzes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，你们俩都来自地球\NSure, you're both from Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们的出生地有天壤之别\Nbut your Kindergartens are radically different.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,等—等等，什么？！\NHold --Hold on. What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都是在地球出生的？\NWe're both from Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.56,0:06:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛，对呀\NWell, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶，你来自主宝宝基地\NAmethyst, you're from the Prime Kindergarten,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,在第五区\Nin Facet 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.86,0:06:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,而她来自副宝宝基地，在第九区\NShe's from the Beta Kindergarten, in Facet 9.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.98,0:06:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你们去过那个地方吗？\NHave you seen that place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,没有！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.07,0:06:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，好吧，你们应该去看看，这样你就能明白\NOh. Well, maybe you should,so you could see
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.62,0:06:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,其他的宝石是怎么做出来的的\Nhow the other half was made.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,粗制滥造！\NPoorly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不，认真的，咱们走吧\NNo, seriously.Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看完你就该释怀了吧\NYou'll get a kick out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的个人问题，波莱特\NThat's your problem,Paulette.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.05,0:06:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是你任由自己变成舠一族的\NYou let yourself become the kayak race.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,太凄凉了\NCold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，给我一秒钟\NUm, just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.97,0:06:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我想确认一下青金石一个人没问题\NI want to check and make sure Lapis is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.98,0:06:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，青金石！你没问题吧？？！\NHey, Lapis!\NAre you okay-y-y?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗？\NAre you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,确定！\NYeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了，但我很快就会回来！\NI'm leavin',but I'll be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.90,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,好！\NOkay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.77,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么东西吗？！\NDo you need anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不需要！\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.36,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在看的是第几季？！\NWhat season is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,第三季！\N3!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,橄榄石，走吧\NPeridot, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,哦对，好\NOkay, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.53,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,工作时间\NBusiness time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道要把它放到哪里的！\NYou know what to do with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们到了，铁石英的出生地，副宝宝基地\NHere we are, Jasper's origin:the Beta Kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的问题吗？\NAm I underwhelmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.38,0:07:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这里亮得刺眼\NIt's pretty bright out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.00,0:07:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,全是红色的\NIt's red.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.51,0:07:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,确实\NNo kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.55,0:07:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,红砂岩！哈！\NRed sandstone! Ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这材料不能更差！\NThis is what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方还没被炸烂也是很幸运\NWe're lucky this place hasn't blown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.47,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,果然只能算“副”，对不对？\NBeta, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么数学玩笑吗？\NThat's a math joke,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,快来吧，这里还会更糟的\NCome on.It get's worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.15,0:07:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，这个地方成长环境还好\NI mean, this place has got the right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也确实难得\Ngrowing conditions,\Nin a pinch,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但它面积太小了！\NI guess,\Nbut it's too small!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这里完全就是赶工做出来的\NIt was obviously a total rush job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.04,0:07:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,赶工？\NA rush job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.99,0:07:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,内战进行到一半的时候\NHalfway through the rebellion,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.63,0:07:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,母星急于在地球上\NHomeworld scrambled to generate
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,制造出更多的士兵\Nextra soldierson the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个:这些洞都没排成直线！\NLook at this: the holes don't even line up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.80,0:07:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,就好像他们只是\NIt's like they just
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.42,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,随随便便找个地方打个孔\Nthrew injectors down wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，再看这个\NOh, and that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这个玛瑙是斜着出来的\NThis Carnelian came out sideways.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,她只能斜着出来！\NHow could she not?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.06,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这些岩壁都是弯的！\NThe walls are curved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,简直可笑\NWhat a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.68,0:08:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,惊了，难以置信\NMan, I-I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你讲，这真的会让感谢\NI tell you, it really makes you appreciate
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,主宝宝基地的，紫晶\Nthe Prime Kindergarten,\NAmethyst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你的宝宝基地很有讲究的\NYour Kindergarten\Nwas so thought-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,是，你可能的确在地下花的时间比较长\NSure, you might've spent\Nextra time in the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但除了这点你其他的先天条件都很优秀\Nbut everything else\Nis stacked in your favor:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不错的地点，不错的出生洞穴\Ngreat location,great holes,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,均匀的空间分配，连贯的洞穴尺寸\Neven spacing,consistent depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,专业宝宝基地工程师才做得好\NA real Kindergartener gets it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.84,0:08:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这个注射器发生了什么？\NWhat happened to this injector?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,理想情况下，洞穴该是垂直的\NWhat you want to see is a vertical alignment;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,出口应该呈现出清晰的轮廓，而不是斜角\Nno angle in the exit;a clean, strong silhouette.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这些洞穴里没有一个达成了指标！\NNone of these holes come close!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这个呢？\NWhat about that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,铁石英\NJasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这是铁石英的洞穴？\NThis is Jasper's hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.05,0:08:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,它可真大！\NIt's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.69,0:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，拜托\NOh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都知道她挺高的\NWe already know she's tall.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我们来近距离瞧一瞧它\NLet's take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.98,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一个宝宝基地工程师最明白——\NA Kindergartener can tell a lot --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！怎样通过洞穴的出口观察——\NAnh! -- about a Gem's makeup and --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.82,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,呃！——宝石的构成和缺陷\NUh! -- flaws by their exit marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.32,0:09:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呜呼！\NOof!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢了\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAgh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧，问题在——\NYou see,the problem here --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.88,0:09:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,等等. 哦，等下，呃\NWait.Oh, wait. Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不，唔…\NNo, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.67,0:09:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方——\NNow this part --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.34,0:09:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但是呢，如果你用脚步来测量\NThere's this thing where,if you count the steps
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,到底的距离，就能——\Nto the back, I can --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.18,0:09:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,她的洞里连摩擦融化石头的痕迹都有\NShe's even got frictional rock melt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.90,0:09:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,从洞口直到洞底都是玻璃的\NIt's glass all the way to the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上，我，呃…\NActually, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.77,0:09:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,从来没见过这么完美的洞穴\NI've never seen an exit hole this perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.99,0:09:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,惹\NUgh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她真的比我好\NSo it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶，这一点都不重要\NAmethyst,that doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.03,0:09:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你是谁不取决于你来自哪里\NWho you are isn't about where you came from;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,取决于你想成为什么！\Nit's who you want to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.81,0:09:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,取决于你努力的方向\NIt's what you've worked hard for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.45,0:09:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,取决于你所重视的事物. 这才是重要的\NIt's what you care about.That's what really matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.53,0:09:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的对！\NYeah, you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-对！-没错！\N-Yeah!-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,取决于我想要成为什么\NIt's about who I wanna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错！-没错！\N-Yeah!-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.46,0:09:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,而我想成为那个宝石\NAnd I wanna be the Gem
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那个把铁石英打的满地找牙的宝石！\Nthat beats Jasper into the dirt!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-没错！什么？！\N-Yeah!-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，别！不要和她打！\NWait, no!Don't fight her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你还不明白吗？\NAre you not seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一个终极的石英战士\NShe's the ultimate Quartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要这么做，没错，不只是为了我自己\NI'm doin' it, yeah,and not just for me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为了所有其他在这里出生的家伙们\Nfor all the weird holes out here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.61,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,比如这个伙计，还有这个小瘦子\Nlike this guy,and skinny up there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.51,0:10:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,还有——还有这个乱七八糟的家伙！\Nand -- and --and this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶，这是——\NAmethyst, that's --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,对，哈！我打赌她肯定挺厉害的\NYeah, ha!I bet she was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.15,0:10:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不不不，等等\NNo.No, no, no, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么地方不对\NSomething's really wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这些痕迹是新的\NThese marks are new.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这个洞穴是最近才被挖开的\NThis hole's been dug out, recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.66,0:10:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会是土拨鼠干的？\NMaybe it was a prairie dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,超大的一只？\NA...really big one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,唔\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,还有更多！\NThere's more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.70,0:10:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,喔啊\NWhoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.67,0:10:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这些已经不是出口洞穴了\NThese aren't exit holes anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那他们是用来干嘛的？\NThen what are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！\NAah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.18,0:10:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文！\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,宝石怪物，被囚禁的？\NCorrupted Gems,in cages?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？！\NWhy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会想要这么做？！\NWho would do this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.52,0:11:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,就是她\NThat's who.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.56,0:11:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,铁石英\NJasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,铁石英！\NJasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.19,0:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她在干嘛呢？\NWhat is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她最近一直在收集宝石怪物\NShe's been collecting monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.48,0:11:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,安静！\NPipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们现在开始要服从我的命令！\NYou take orders from me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你曾经也是颗石英，不是吗？\NYou used to be a quartz, too,didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.72,0:11:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,在你身上发生了什么？\NWhat happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,呃！肮脏\NUgh!Disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不敢相信我居然收下你这种怪物做手下！\NI can't believe I've resorted to recruiting you freaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你和水晶战士中的那个矮子一样糟糕\NYou're almost as bad as that crystal runt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你\NJust look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这个星球毁掉了一切\NThis planet ruins everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧，除了我\NWell except for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该回神庙里叫上其他人\NWe should go back to the temple and grab reinforcements.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,对，这是个好主意\NYeah,that's a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶？\NAmethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶！\NAmethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远不会让这颗星球像扭曲你这样毁掉我\NI'll never let this planet twist me like it twisted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.85,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脆弱让母星蒙羞\NYour weakness embarrasses Homeworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的痛苦都是你自找的\NYou suffer because it's what you deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们身上发生的都理所应当\NWe all only get what we deserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对不对，紫晶？\NRight, Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.20,0:12:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.79,0:12:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你来这里做什么，矮子？\NWhat do you want,runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要再次挑战我？\NYou here for a rematch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我是来打败你的！\NI'm here to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你出场的瞬间，已经注定会输了\NYou were fated to lose --the moment you came out wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你胡说！\NThat's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,玫瑰，果不其然\NRose.Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你的走狗在你也不会太远的\NYour lackeys never stray far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,当然他们也不会离开你的\NAnd why would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.22,0:12:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,因为其他任何地方他们都没有立足之处了！\NThey have no place in this or any world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么意思？\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.86,0:12:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,每个宝石都是为了某种目的而制造出的——\NEvery gem is made for a purpose --
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.23,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,为了服侍钻石的圣旨\Nto serve the order of the diamonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那些无法完成钻石命令的必须被清除！\NThose who cannot fit inside this order must be purged!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,出生时畸形的体态\NTo come out misshapen,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,按照自己意愿胡乱变形\Nto reshape yourself outside your purpose,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,保护这个无药可救，没用的星球\Nand to defend this ruined,worthless planet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这些都是耻辱！\Nis a disgrace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这颗星球也没那么糟\NThis planet isn't all bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛呢？\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我…\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在也是个水晶战士了！\NI'm a crystal gem now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我不怕你！\NI'm not afraid of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在有金属能力了！\NI've got metal powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.22,0:13:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞧着吧！\NI'll show you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.68,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊老天\NAw, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.14,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NIn a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,还有人有要说的吗？\NAnyone else got something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.36,0:13:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不！没有别人了\NNo!It's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.21,0:13:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,呃！你们！\NUgh!You guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈？！-别来凑热闹了！\N-Huh?!-Stay out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶！\NAmethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.36,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是咱俩间的事，铁石英——\NIt's just you and me,Jasper --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一对一！\None on one!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.76,0:13:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,上，紫晶！\NGo, Amethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在谁是矮子了？\NWho's the runt now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好了？\NYou ready for more?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,还——还有别的招数呢\NTh-- There's more where that came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊哦\N-Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,哈？\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.07,0:14:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了吗？\NIs it sinking in yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗？！\NAre you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.08,0:14:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,紫晶！\NAmethyst!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你从未有过机会\NYou never had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,¶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.30,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抬头！\NHeads up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,-哈？-哈？\N-Huh?-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.01,0:14:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文，我赢不了\NSteven I can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,无论我做什么，无论我多么努力\NNo matter what I do,no matter how hard I work,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她生来完美，我生来卑微\Nshe came out right,and I came out wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.65,0:14:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是铁石英认为的\NThat's just what Jasper thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.22,0:14:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只有她觉得你本应该像她一样\NShe's the only one who thinks you should be like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,-但是-不要再试图变得和铁石英一样了\N-But -Stop trying to be like Jasper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你和铁石英完全不同！\NYou're nothing like Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你更像我——\NYou're like me --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.23,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们都是这样格格不入\Nbecause we're both not like anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊，这是挺糟糕的\NAnd, yeah, it sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,但至少我还有你\NBut at least I've got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你也有我\NAnd you've got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.87,0:15:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不要再抛下我一个人战斗了\NSo stop leaving me out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,最糟的宝石总得呆在一起不是吗？\NUs worst gems stick together right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这也是为什么我们是最棒的\NThat's why we're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.73,0:15:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,¶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,多么美好的一天！\NWhat a beautiful day!w
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哈?你是谁？\NHuh?!Who are you supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦对啊，我现在是谁来着?\NOh, yeah!Who am I now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想紫晶应该知道我是谁\NI feel like Amethyst knows this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.76,0:05:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,先别管你的名字了--你还有一场架要干呢\NForget your name --you've got a fight to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我想一个玫瑰石英和一个紫水晶\NI think a rose quartz and an amethyst...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在一起就是\N…make a...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,烟晶\N...Smoky Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们水晶宝石难道现在只懂融合这招吗\NIs fusion the only trick you crystal gems know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,嘛我懂的招式还真不少\NI've got plenty of tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,见过【前抛】没有\NEver see sink the dink?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我的军队\NMy army!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,哈糊你一脸\NTake that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再吃我这招\NThen take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 这么快就要离开啦\NAw. Leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会再败在融合上了\NI will not be beaten by another fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.05,0:06:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,什么鬼\NWhat the...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.83,0:06:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\NHold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我还真有个可以把你干飞的招\NI've got a move that will really blow you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你不喜欢也没关系\NIt's cool if you don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经准备了三个大风扇啦\NI've already got three huge fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只要坚持在一起…就可以打败她们\NWe could beat them... if we stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,干的漂亮 小烟\NGreat job, Smoky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.77,0:07:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 谢谢 谢了 小烟\NOh, thank you, thank you, Smoky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.14,0:07:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我融合的人从来没有愿意留下的\NNobody I fuse with ever wants to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,噫 超恶心啦\NEw! That's disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.93,0:07:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是堕转\NIt's corruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.07,0:07:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文 小心啊\NSteven, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.61,0:07:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我不能眼睁睁地看着它发生\NBut this just happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我可以做些什么\NMaybe I can do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,铁石英 没事的\NJasper, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.01,0:08:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这里\NI'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,玫瑰\NRose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.55,0:08:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是玫瑰 我是史蒂文\NI'm not Rose. I'm Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在只想试着治愈你\NI just want to try and heal you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.86,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,史蒂文\NSteven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.07,0:08:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么 别冲动\NWhat? Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在知道你的把戏了\NI see how you do it now, Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你在宝石人失去价值后再去收她们入伙 \NYou want gems after they're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直等到她们失败才动手\NYou wait until after they've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.01,0:08:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为当你到了最倒霉的时候\NBecause when you're at the bottom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就会顺从于从任何人\Nyou'll follow anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这会减轻你的挫败感\NThat makes you feel like less of a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.26,0:08:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 就看看这个家伙\NUgh. Just look at this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你剥夺了她的一切 --\NYou've stripped her of everything --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她的扩增肢，她的地位，她的尊严\Nher limb enhancers, her status, her dignity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有一样呢\NI still have one of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么可以站在玫瑰石英那边\NHow can you side with Rose Quartz?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.74,0:09:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要保护这个没用的空壳行星\NWhy protect this useless shell of a planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,它不是一个空壳\NIt's not a shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这里还有数不胜数的生命\NThere's so much life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,生活 --这就是我在这里做的事啊\NLiving here -- that's what I'm doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.08,0:09:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我生活在这里\NI'm living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我每时每刻都在了解自己未发掘的潜能\NI've been learning new things about myself all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.55,0:09:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,比如现在我可以让金属都顺从我的旨意\Nlike how I can make metal do my bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,重点是…\NThe point being...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.76,0:09:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,地球可以给你自由\NEarth can set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,地球…就是一个监牢\NEarth...is a prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我之所以可以离开是因为我远远优于这个鬼地方\NI got out because I'm better than this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,情况在恶化\NIt's getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.30,0:09:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来就是为了结果你们\NI only came back to finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.57,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,尽量不要动\NTry not to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你休想操控我 玫瑰石英\NYou can't manipulate me, Rose Quartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.11,0:09:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我-我不是想操控你\NI-I'm not manipulating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想帮忙\NI'm -- I'm trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙\NHelp?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,帮忙\NHelp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,自我从这地壳破土而出\NI've been fighting
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我就一直在战斗\Nfrom the second I broke free of the Earth's crust
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,只因你对我的殖民地做的事\Nbecause of what you did to my colony,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.59,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只因你对我的星球所做的事\Nbecause of what you did to my planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.93,0:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,只因你对我的钻石所做的事\Nbecause of what you did to my diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我 --你说黄钻？\NI -- Yellow Diamond?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我的钻石！\NMy diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你的钻石！\NYour diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.87,0:10:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,粉红钻石！\NPink diamond!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.06,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢哈\NYou're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 老姐\NCome here, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,当我们回到谷仓后\NWhen we get to the barn,
